snippet.title: Combat Chess gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Combat Chess, PC game produced by Empire Interactive in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/combat-chess/13090/
Combat Chess is very interesting chess game with sensational graphics with medieval pieces; dragons and colorfully attired rooks, knights, bishops, kings and queens.
Played through modern Windows machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Ed Chess - https://youtu.be/D41pYzEXNwI
Battle Chess (MPC version) - https://youtu.be/V1H7FYvfLy8
Chess 88 - https://youtu.be/OgpvEw5Lfj8
